.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/REB6R70</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ixquaPandaJumper]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>So mad</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KB6iR7n</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kmx9FpO.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KB6iR7n</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[candiedyms]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Every man's dream!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/iNMkrai</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JgUaiDm.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/iNMkrai</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CityYeti]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Illustrator extraordinaire Mark Fredrickson does tour poster for Weird Al - THIS is art!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/igowSdi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MQHjAAK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/igowSdi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[exactchangeman]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Still here. War is still raging. Appreciate all the international help though.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/chjLtIY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gDxuoiI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Morning coffee</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/R7R4rvB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Made a lot of fortifications lately</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HlCD71V.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s cozy, if not for mice running across my face at night.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XPDRUMP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My new pal</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1HxICFi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My mate with some gear we’ve got from volunteers</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zBHFLlE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This dude is almost 70. He’s the most efficient dude in our platoon.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lpYrsb4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>That’s why you shouldn’t buy cheap plates</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7XlAEfm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The weather is better each day. I’ve also been promoted to a Sargent. And I have 10 subordinates now.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ozlrSyc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I lived here for quite some time</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XygqFRS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pnOzC2E.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Some soup</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vUZswr9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My dumbbells(20 kg/44 lbs each)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YVISg4c.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Our dining place)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/84i281a.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>FRONT PAGE CLARIFICATION!  Guys, I don’t want to get money from you for nothing. I just wasn’t raised to be able do so. I am trying to sell this, to make money for a good cause. Not just receive it for free. As a journalist, I’ve never worked so much in my life. I’m building, digging, cutting down trees, training my mates. And that’s not including my direct shoot, move, communicate duties. But you’re not getting any of this. So it would be unfair to get anything from you. I appreciate all the offers, but I just can’t accept them.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/chjLtIY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[EliBLifter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Right?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xLvjud5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cR876xv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xLvjud5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[angelinesg7]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>such a comedian...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/876oatV</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5RNbUY2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/876oatV</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[shelworth]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This is Loki the golden retriever and he is a happy boy :)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/jGHfOBe</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Mk7a4Fz.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Source : https://instagram.com/lokiretrievers</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/jGHfOBe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Rammsteinstochter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Is this true?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tBi5poh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nz7irSG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tBi5poh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheBigLetdown]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Shaqasize it</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uwyMVud</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/